title: Asif Ali Zardari wins NA-207 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarian (PPPP) Candidate Asif Ali Zardari has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-207 Shaheed Benazirabad-I by securing 1,46,989 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Sardar Sher Muhammad Rind Baloch, who bagged 51,916 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 44.52 percent.
